authorities detained a U.S. citizen with alleged ties to
Hezbollah, designated a terrorist organization by the U.S. State
Department, Mexico City-based newspaper  El Universal  reported.  Authorities detained Rafic Mohammad Labboun Allaboun in the
Yucatan state city of Merida and handed him over to U.S.
authorities on Sunday, the newspaper reported on its website
